      "layout": "The page adheres to a full-bleed layout, maximizing the impact of the deep black canvas. The hero section features a large, horizontally centered headline over a background that interacts with a large abstract green circle. Sections maintain a consistent vertical rhythm, primarily composed of centered text blocks. Content primarily arranges in single columns for direct readability, with navigation elements positioned in the top corners for a balanced, minimalist visual structure. The layout prioritizes ample negative space, creating an uncluttered and focused experience.",
